        <mxCell id="RMAH8zwnuNR-1aBGTGTo-22" value="&lt;h1&gt;Routing to Filecoin&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;DEMOS SDK enables users and developers to leverage the battle-proven, reliable and secure storage service provided by Filecoin regardless of the original context.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Every Storage Based or related operation is routed through Filecoin thanks to its integration with DEMOS.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;spacing=5;spacingTop=-20;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
